          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2020-07-17T21:37:01Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution (1) condemns the tweet made by the President on October 22, 2019, drawing a moral equivalence between the exercise of the impeachment power conferred on the House of Representatives by the Constitution and lynching; and (2) calls upon all Americans to read, celebrate, and revere the Constitution.</p> <ul> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-11-22T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
